      ],
      "source": "https://www.westfieldnj.com/whs/history/prospectpark.htm"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Revolutionary leaders, including General Lafayette, used the Dey House as a temporary headquarters while traveling Cannonball Road.",
